release.notes: First release
Fixed some security hole and changed base language from Japanese to English on the pc_frontend.
Added an ability to render iframes of the outer OpenSocial container and fixed the PersistentAPI.
This version is compatible with Doctrine.
The preseted profile item was made to correspond to API
Fixed MemberApplicationSetting model, because index key is too long.
Added an ability for Albums API.
Added an ability to approve install of the app from SNS admin.
Added Activity API and an ability to request share app.
Add an ability for the lifecycle-event.
Support Mobile App
Fixed some bug on the mobile.
Supported location service, and added an ability to extend url of replacing on the mobile.
Stable release for OpenPNE3.6
fixed JSON-RPC API because friend data can't be fetched.
Added some tests for security countermeasures.

Fixed the following bugs. #1828: [pc][mobile] Fatal error in application/invite when a member has no friend #2021: [pc] Fix the response /application/invite #2022: [api] PHP Notice in "lib_for_shindig/OpenPNEService.php" #2023: [pc] "home" view doesn't exists #2026: [etc] opOpenSocial:execute-lifecycle-event タスクの limit-request オプションで指定した値を守らない場合がある #2029: [pc] opShindigRemoteContentFetcher doesn't send header correctly set #2032: [mobile] Container doesn't send a location header when an external server sent a location header #2034: [api] PersistentAPI doesn't return all key-value pair #2035: [pc] gadgets.container._parseIframeUrl doesn't return first parameter correctly #2038: [pc] 招待完了時に正しいレスポンスが返されない #2039: [pc] Fix a mistake of the relayUrl in gadget component

Fixed issues: #2075: [api] /mediaitems/@me/@self/{albumId} で取得できるコレクションの albumId フィールドの値が間違っている #2098: [api] opOpenSocialProfileExport doesn't return birthday when public flag of birthday is '3' and owner is viewer #2101: [pc] modalboxを2回目以降に表示すると、読み込みが完了するまで前回表示時の内容が残ってしまう #2131: [pc] gadget doesn't drive because it occur error that "html4" is not defined (1.2.x only) #2146: [api] /albums/@me/@self で取得したアルバムのサムネイルが未設定の場合 thumbnailUrl フィールドに間違った値が入る #2210: [etc] NOTICE ファイルの更新 #2213: [pc] Fix a js error in application/invite when the user doesn't have any friend (フレンドが0人の時に招待画面で JavaScript エラー) #2215: [pc] Fix two js errors in application/list screen when the user doesn't have any application (所有アプリが 0 件の時に アプリ一覧画面で JavaScript エラー)
Fixed the following issues. #2246: [api] 取得したアクティビティのフィールドに含まれるURLがおかしい #2248: [api] 取得したアクティビティのリンク先URLが streamUrl に格納されている
Fixed the following bug. #2350: [etc] 部分一致検索を行う箇所でワイルドカード検索ができてしまう
Disabled xml external entity loader (OPSA-2013-003)
